  "comment": "SlimBANK Q18 ILS is a versatile quad-color (RGBA) LED wash light with brilliant eye candy effects. It features ILS compatibility with the cutting-edge Integrated Lighting System (ILS) that makes creating coordinated light shows across different fixture types easy. Control options include D-Fi USB compatibility for wireless Master/Slave or DMX control and access to built-in automated programs via IRC-6 remote. This light makes it easy to generate complex looks easily with built-in, eye-catching auto programs with sectional control. Adjustable barn doors help direct and focus the light. SlimBANK Q18 ILS has built-in dimming curves for smooth LED fading and is ideal for sound-sensitive environments due to its radiant cooling design.",
